        "JAVANGLE_HOUSE_TYPHOONUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "The House: Grao-Mastery",
        "JAVANGLE_HOUSE_TYPHOONUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESC": "Como The House, gana el juego o arrasa en Tufao.",
